---
import { CircleCheckBig, Heart, Linkedin } from "@lucide/astro";
import GithubIcon from "../../components/icons/GithubIcon.astro";
---

<section class="py-3 px-2 sm:px-6 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[360px] sm:max-w-[668px]">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-10">
      <img src="/logo/openlane-logo-dark.svg" alt="Openlane Logo" class="dark:hidden max-w-none" />
      <img src="/logo/openlane-logo-light.svg" alt="Openlane Logo" class="hidden dark:block max-w-none" />
    </a>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-2xl leading-9 letter-spacing-[-0.75px] font-normal text-color mb-3 md:mb-10">
      We’re building Openlane in the open: a modern, developer-first toolkit for security and compliance. No lock-in, no black boxes. Just code, community, and clear intent.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-2xl leading-9 letter-spacing-[-0.75px] font-normal text-color mb-3 md:mb-10">
      We’d love your support — GitHub stars, small sponsorships, and contributions go a long way. Our early access waitlist is open too.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-5 mb-5 md:mt-10 md:mb-10">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/theopenlane/core"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-xs sm:text-sm w-[180px] font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary text-invert-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap hover:bg-brand-300 !transition-colors !duration-300"
      >
        <GithubIcon width="19" height="19" /> Star Github repo
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://github.com/sponsors/theopenlane"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-xs sm:text-sm w-[180px] font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary text-invert-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap hover:bg-brand-300 !transition-colors !duration-300"
      >
        <Heart size={19} /> Sponsor on Github
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/theopenlane/"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-xs sm:text-sm w-[180px] font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary text-invert-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap hover:bg-brand-300 !transition-colors !duration-300"
      >
        <Linkedin size={19} /> Follow on LinkedIn
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mb-20 mt-2 block sm:hidden">
      <p class="text-sm text-support">Scroll for more</p>
      <div class="scroll-down-container">
        <div class="scroll-down-wrapper">
          <div class="scroll-down-anim"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-start text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <CircleCheckBig class="text-color-primary w-[14px] md:w-[20px] mt-1 shrink-0" />
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-xl leading-7">Built so you can run it, but we're here to do it for you</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <CircleCheckBig class="text-color-primary w-[14px] md:w-[20px] mt-1 shrink-0" />
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-xl leading-7">GraphQL APIs, Go-native code, and open source end-to-end</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <CircleCheckBig class="text-color-primary w-[14px] md:w-[20px] mt-1 shrink-0" />
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-xl leading-7">Everything’s open, documented, and ready for contributors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mb-10 mt-10 hidden sm:block">
      <p class="text-sm text-support">Scroll for more</p>
      <div class="scroll-down-container">
        <div class="scroll-down-wrapper">
          <div class="scroll-down-anim"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .text-support {
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .scroll-down-container {
    top: 30px;
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    transition: 0.5s;
    transition-delay: 0s;
    transition-duration: 1.5s;
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: all;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .scroll-down-wrapper {
    width: 5px;
    padding: 10px 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border: 2px solid #9ca3af;
    border-radius: 2.5em;
    box-sizing: content-box;
    margin: 0 auto 0 auto;
    transition: transform 0.25s;
  }

  .scroll-down-anim {
    height: 5px;
    width: 2px;
    border-radius: 0.3em;
    margin: inherit;
    border: 1px solid #9ca3af;
    animation-name: scroll-animation;
    animation-duration: 2.2s;
    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.15, 0.41, 0.69, 0.94);
    animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    background-color: #9ca3af;
  }

  @keyframes scroll-animation {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
    }

    10% {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }

    100% {
      transform: translateY(15px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
